In Islamic philosophy, '''Wahdat al-Mawjud''' is the opposite of [[Wahdat al-wujud]]. It is the concept that existence moves towards Spiritual oneness, but remains plural. Eventually human beings become ''İnsan-ı Kâmil and reach wisdom of god (Anal Haqq).''

